===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|cirurgien}}, borrowed from {{der|en|fro|cirurgiien}}, itself borrowed from {{der|en|VL.|*chīrurgiānus}} or formed from the root of {{m|fro|cirurgie}}, borrowed from {{der|en|la|chirurgia}}, ultimately from {{der|en|grc|χειρουργός}}. More at {{l|en|surgeon}}, {{l|en|surgery}}.

